# flounder
flounder is a library that create Entity of Dialogflow.
This library uses RestAPI of dialogflow. It is not an official library.

## Installation

### flounder requires:

```
pip install git+https://github.com/miurahr/pykakasi.git
```

### install flounder:

```
pip install flounder
```
